» Commercial Real Estate Agent Required on Commission Basis – Ros Invest Real Estate – Dubai Jobs
Posted on 06 May 2014. Tags: , , , , , , , , ,
ROS INVEST REAL ESTATE – THE ART OF PROPERTY MANAGEMENT
We are looking for real estate agents.
OUR MISSION – Our business was established to connect the desire of investors to benefit with a wide range of possibilities at Dubai real estate market.
Our Advantages:* Bonuses upon reaching the target* Attractive commission based contract. *Certified Real Estate Broker Training in Dubai Real Estate Institute* Brand-new office facilities (your personal work space)* Convenient office location (Al Barsha 1 – opposite site of Wellington School)* Company visa and Labor card* 100% legal employment status as per UAE laws* Fully optimized Web portal* Full marketing support – Regular advertising at REAL ESTATE portals!* Property Support (direct contacts)* Strong motivated and friendly team
Key Responsibilities:* Planning and organizing meetings with new and existing clients* Property viewings for prospect clients* Advertising properties for Sale and Lease* Finding new clients* Be able to advice client on legal rights,
market conditions,
valuation,
transfer requirements and other aspects of Real Estate market in DubaiOur Requirements:* Self-Motivated,
Self organized and Goal oriented* Working experience in Dubai is the must * Driving license and personal car is preferable* Good English (written and verbally) is required* Knowledge of main freehold areas
If you are fit our requirements,
able to perform key responsibilities and wish to receive all advantages of working in Real Estate Field,
please send us CV on the link below
